# Third-Party Attributions

This project uses third-party fonts and assets. All assets are properly licensed for HTTPS use.

For complete attribution details, see [ATTRIBUTIONS.md](../ATTRIBUTIONS.md) in the root directory.

## Quick Reference

- **Fonts**: All fonts use SIL Open Font License (OFL) Version 1.1
- **Images**: Proprietary assets owned by Macro Marketing
- **Dependencies**: All npm packages are MIT or compatible licenses

All licenses are compliant with HTTPS deployment requirements.
